$ Microsoft.SqlServer.Dts.Runtime.Task (abstract class)
@ Microsoft.SqlServer.Dts.Runtime.Task

`Microsoft.SqlServer.Dts.Runtime.Task` defines the properties and methods that are common to all tasks in integration services.

`Task` inherits from `Microsoft.SqlServer.Dts.Runtime.DtsObject` and has the following classes that derive from it:
